SUMMARY:Steve Flemming's Love Songs that Stir the Soul 
DESCRIPTION:Try New Things in Toronto!\nHello everyone\,\n\nPlease join us
  **on zoom** for a fun\, relaxing and inspiring evening with **Love Songs 
 that Stir the Soul.**\n\nSongs that I have written for well over 36 years.
 \nYou will love what you hear! :)\nNew songs every week\, including some o
 f our favorites!\n\n\\*You are welcome to join us any time after 8:30 pm (
 Eastern Time)\n\\*You are also welcome to come on later in the evening as 
 well\n**\\*\\*Attend for free if you like - if it's your first time attend
 ing :)**\n\nEvent Details below:\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Songwr
 iter/Producer/Host)\n\nEvent Details:\n**Steve Flemming's Love Songs that 
 Stir the Soul**\n**(on Zoom)**\n\n\\*Original Lyrics and Songs by Songwrit
 er and Producer Steve Flemming\n\n\\*Story songs\, love songs\, spiritual 
 songs\, songs about nature\, our culture\, our past\, our future\, relatio
 nships and our lives\n\nI'll be playing a mix of songs using a fusion of m
 ixed genres like\, **Folk\, Traditional Folk\, Country\, Blue Grass\, Sing
 er Song Writer\, Soft Rock\, Easy Listening\, Classic Rock\, R & B\, Gospe
 l\, Pop\, Adult Contemporary\, Indie Rock/Po**p and many others genres too
 . So please sit back and get ready to have an amazing auditory experience 
 in the comforts of your own home :)\n\n\\*You can come on and off at any t
 ime during the night- starting at 8:30 pm\n\n**About Steve Flemming:**\nHi
 ghly influenced by the great singer songwriters of the 50s\, 60s\, 70s\, 8
 0s and 90s. I have been writing my own songs since 1990. Songs about life\
 , love\, loss\, hope\, faith\, joy\, romance\, memories\, spirituality and
  heartbreak. Songs that are universal\, heartfelt and often relevant to th
 e lives of many others.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Event Fee:**\n\n**P
 ay What You Can: (P.W.Y.C)**\nYou can kindly send through e transfer or pa
 y pal to:\n**steveflemming11@gmail.com**\n\n-Anything you can contribute i
 s greatly appreciated to help support this meaningful musical endeavor and
  song loving community\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Zoom link:**\n\nhttps://us04web.zoom.us/j/4
 95043928\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\n\n**Testimonials from Past Events:**\nYour songs are wonder-full\, spe
 ak to emotions\, experiences and moments we've all felt and lived. S. B.\n
 Steve Flemming is an amazing songwriter whose lyrics stir the soul. He tra
 nsforms everyday thoughts and life into beautiful poetry and magical tunes
 . Amazing stuff yet again Steve. - L.L.\nSteve\, thank you for a night of 
 heartfelt\, exhilarating\, and inspiring music.\nV.R.\nThanks for having m
 e my friend. I love your words\, they calm me and energize me at the same 
 time I'll look forward to your next invite\nM.Z.\nThese great songs defini
 tely helped me to decompress after a long day. Keep up the song writing St
 eve\, these are great! - S.S.\nThank you so much for a relaxing evening an
 d sharing your inspiring music Steve! I am excited to hear more and I hope
  you do this again!! - C.B\nLovely songs and a great vibe with wonderful p
 eople. I couldn’t have asked for a better way to close my day. Huge than
 ks Steve\, for inviting me! I truly enjoyed every moment! - N.A.\nThe lyri
 cs are amazing. From the heart...\nThanks Steve for the amazing tunes. I'm
  truly blown away. Very glad I joined.\n\\- E\\.E\\.\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-
